For testing purposes on the development machine, use virtualenv.

Test by doing the following:
1. Extract distribution tarbell to folder on Desktop
2. Switch to newly create folder with extracted distribution
3. Run virtualenv

virtualenv uploader-test
cd uploader-test
source bin/activate

4. Switch back to newly created folder with extracted distribution and run setup.py

cd ..
python setup.py install

5. Run tests

./apple-mail-uploader.py

6. When done, exit out of virtual environment with:

deactivate

